## About The Project

This project simply emulates "The Matrix"-effect on any console-terminal.

### Made With
[![Python][MadeWith-Python]](https://www.python.org/)

<p align="right">(<a href="#top">back to top</a>)</p>

## Getting Started

### Prerequisites

It is neccessary that a font is installed, which supports the unicode characters used (greek, hebrew, cyrillic).

### Installation

1. install the python package ([PyPI-cmdtrix](https://pypi.org/project/cmdtrix/)):
```console
pip install cmdtrix
```
<p align="right">(<a href="#top">back to top</a>)</p>

## Usage

```console
cmdtrix [-h] [-c COLOR]
```

